nrest-central-kowloon-ended-railway?utm_source=rss_feed<author><![CDATA[Brian Wong]]></author><category>消息</category><category>香港</category><category>香港法院</category><category>香港抗议活动</category><category>香港地铁</category><category>香港罪案</category><category>犯罪</category><category>法律</category><category>香港抗议活动：三人因九龙中部骚乱导致火车站混乱而被判入狱长达 5.5 年</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[As Beijing seeks to revive private sector, officials in one Chinese city urge ‘soft approach’ to minor offences]]></title><description><![CDATA[<p>中国中部城市的政府官员本月初表示，频繁且不可预测的政策变化可能会扼杀民营企业，在处理轻微违法行为时应采取“人道”和“软”的方式非国有部门推动了低迷的经济。</p><p> “对于企业家来说，经营一家初创企业是一件生死攸关的事情，”河南省工业城市洛阳的官员在微信上发布的一份报告中说。 “频繁且不可预测的政策变化对企业不利。它们会阻止潜在的创业者，并对商业环境产生巨大影响。” </p><div class="meter__linear relative" id="default-meter-page-views-11"><img width="auto" height="1" src="https://www.scmp.com/images/1x1.png" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="dm__l3"><hr class="vertical-line"><div class="dm__lw"><svg class="dm__l" height="24" viewBox="0 0 18 24" width="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g style="stroke:#000;fill:none;fill-rule:evenodd;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;stroke-width:1.5"><rect height="13.5" rx="1.5" width="16.5" x=".75" y="9.75"></rect><path d="m3.75 9.75v-3.75c0-2.89949494 2.35050506-5.25 5.25-5.25 2.8994949 0 5.25 2.35050506 5.25 5.25v3.75"></path><path d="m9.00000067 15.75c-.20710745 0-.37500067.1678932-.37500067.3749993 0 .2071075.16789322.3750007.37500067.3750007.20710611 0 .37499933-.1678932.37499933-.3750007.0002665-.0995369-.03915673-.1950746-.10954072-.2654586-.070384-.070384-.16592164-.1098072-.26545861-.1095407z"></path></g></svg></div></div><div class="dm__b center-block"><div><div class="dm__h mb-16">您已达到免费文章数量限制。</div><div class="dm__t center-block">订阅 SCMP 以无限制地访问我们屡获殊荣的新闻</div><div class="dm__s2 mt-30"><div class="dm__sb" id="subscribe-btn-11-large" role="button" tabindex="0" subscriptions-action="subscribe" subscriptions-service="subscribe.google.com" subscriptions-display